name: FNF Tankman Test (Bot Studio)
description:
Tankman from week 7 from Friday Night Funkin! Go crazy with his beeps and bops!

Controls: 

Arrow keys to play the sounds

Hold space and right arrow for a combo sound

Hold the Alt key for Ugh!

Check out the Friday Night Funkin here: https://ninja-muffin24.itch.io/funkin
